                                <li>Data Transformation: Converts between formats (JSON, XML, ISO 20022).</li>
                                <li>Legacy Integration: Bridges modern and legacy systems.</li>
                                <li>Error Handling: Implements dead letter queues for failed messages.</li>
                            </ul>
